product: Amazon.com: Customer reviews: Rayboen for Samsung Galaxy A32 5G Case Diamond Clear Designed [Anti-Yellowing] Shockproof Phone Case, Hard Back & Soft TPU Bumper Hybrid Transparent Cover for Galaxy A32 5G Phone Case 6.5 inch
title: Good fit, good cutouts and buttons
body: The case fit perfectly - in fact, it was a bit hard to take off so I could add a new screen protector (note, this case does not include the screen protector). That tells me that the case is likely to stay on the phone. The cutouts are perfectly placed, and I especially like the buttons that look and feel like... well, like buttons. Very pleased with this purchase.
